NAME
    Dancer::Plugin::SecureSessionID - Dancer-Plugin-SecureSessionID

VERSION
    Version 0.01

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin overrides the `build_id()' method in
    Dancer::Session::Abstract and make use of Crypt::Random to get really
    secure random session ids.

AUTHOR
    David Zurborg, `<zurborg@cpan.org>'

